# Scoring Logic Rules

## Formula
Total = Σ(Score_i × Weight_i / 5 × 100)
- Score_i: raw 1-5 per dimension
- Weight_i: importance weight (Σ = 1.0, MVP = 1/9 each)

## Integrity Gate (Dimension 9)
BINARY MULTIPLIER. If Dimension 9 score = 1 (retraction/ethical breach found):
→ Total Score = 0. No exceptions. No override.

## Grade Mapping
- 90-100: A (Highly Recommended / Alpha Tier)
- 80-89:  B (Recommended / Beta Tier)
- 70-79:  C (Neutral / Gamma Tier)
- 60-69:  D (Not Recommended / Delta Tier)
- <60:    F (Rejected / Omega Tier)

## Origin Traceability
Every score MUST link to origin_snippet — the API response or PDF text that produced it.
